After `simp`, the goal becomes `rw_bisim (Exp.eval e) (Exp.eval (to_cs c))`.
The hypothesis `h` is transformed into `rw_bisim (Exp.eval c) (Exp.eval (to_cs c))`.

The subsequent tactics are:
