Now we have `h4 : Clap.bits2num p lt w args = (2 ^ w - 1 : ZMod p)`.
From `h2 : e.eval = Clap.bits2num p lt w args`, we have `e.eval = (2 ^ w - 1 : ZMod p)`.
Therefore `e.eval.val = (2 ^ w - 1 : ZMod p).val`.
But `(2 ^ w - 1 : ZMod p).val = (2^w : Nat) - 1`.
So `e.eval.val = (2^w : Nat) - 1`.
But `e.eval.val Ôëą 2^w`. This is a contradiction because `(2^w : Nat) - 1 < (2^w : Nat)`.

